        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
          Struggling with disorganized finances? We'll clean up your books, implement proper accounting systems, and establish reliable monthly reporting.
        </p>
        <a href="#contact" class="text-primary-500 font-medium hover:text-primary-600 inline-flex items-center">
          Get Help
